ategory:2011 England riots| ]]\n[[Category:2011 in the United Kingdom]]\n[[Category:Arson in the United Kingdom]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:August 2011 crimes]]\n[[Category:2011 disasters in the United Kingdom]]\n[[Category:August 2011 events in the United Kingdom]]\n[[Category:Looting]]\n[[Category:Riots in London]]\n", "name_user": "PeterAnderszewski", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eMainstream media relationship with the communities:a study taking account of the perspective of those who live in the \"riot-hit\" areas", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2011_England_riots"}
