o|Poko]]}}}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Bruno Zita Mbanangoy\u00e9|Mbanangoy\u00e9]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[\u00c9ric Mouloungui|Mouloungui]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{penmiss}} [[Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang|Aubameyang]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Bruno Ecuele Manga|Manga]]}}\n|align=left| [[Didier Ovono|D. Ovono]]\n|rowspan=2| [[2012 Africa Cup of Nations|2012, Gabon/Equatorial Guinea]]\n|{{Hs|1}} [[2012 Africa Cup of Nations#Quarter-finals|Quarter-finals]]\n|{{dts|format=dmy|2012-02-05}}\n|-\n| {{nts|24}}.\n| {{fb|ZAM}}\n|align=center| [[2012 Africa Cup of Nations Final|0\u20130]]\n| {{fb|CIV}}\n| {{CNone|'''8\u20137'''}}\n|align=center| 1\u20132\n|align=center| 9\u20139\n|align=right| [[Kennedy Mweene|Mweene]]\n|align=right style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|[[Christopher Katongo|C. Katongo]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Emmanuel Mayuka|Mayuka]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Isaac Chansa|Chansa]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Felix Katongo|F. Katongo]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Kennedy Mweene|Mweene]] {{pengoal}}}}\n----\n{{nowrap|[[Nathan Sinkala|Sinkala]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Chisamba Lungu|Chisamba]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Rainford Kalaba|Kalaba]] {{penmiss}}}}<br>{{nowrap|{{font color||gold|[[Stophira Sunzu|Sunzu]] {{pengoal}}}}}}\n|align=left style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|{{font color||#C3C3C3|{{pengoal}} [[Cheick Tiot\u00e9|Tiot\u00e9]]}}}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Wilfried Bony|Bony]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Sol Bamba|Bamba]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Max Gradel|Gradel]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Didier Drogba|Drogba]]}}\n----\n{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Siaka Ti\u00e9n\u00e9|Ti\u00e9n\u00e9]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Didier Ya Konan|Ya Konan]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{penmiss}} [[Kolo Tour\u00e9|K. Tour\u00e9]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{penmiss}} [[Gervinho]]}}\n|align=left| [[Boubacar Barry|Barry]]\n|{{Hs|1}} [[2012 Africa Cup of Nations#Final|Final]]\n|{{dts|format=dmy|2012-02-12}}\n|-\n| {